264
00:12:55,986 --> 00:12:58,354
One book, my choice.

265
00:13:11,101 --> 00:13:12,435
Wow.

266
00:13:12,535 --> 00:13:14,470
That had to hurt.

267
00:13:14,570 --> 00:13:19,075
