274
00:13:30,987 --> 00:13:33,056
Look, this should have been
handled a long time ago.

275
00:13:33,156 --> 00:13:35,225
Take it easy, okay?
It's a misunderstanding.

276
00:13:35,325 --> 00:13:37,560
Bettye, call that kid
in the film office I talked to.

277
00:13:37,660 --> 00:13:40,330
Kevin something.
Yeah.

278
00:13:40,430 --> 00:13:42,899
